articles.description: Marvin Bagley III had 33 points and 17 rebounds, Grayson Allen made his first five 3-pointers and No. 5 Duke rolled to an 88-70 victory over Notre Dame in the Atlantic Coast Conference Tournament quarterfinals Thursday night.
articles.headline: Bagley, No. 5 Duke rout Notre Dame 88-70 in ACC tourney

articles.headline: Temple avoids upset, holds off Tulane 82-77 in AAC 1st round
